org.apache.ambari.server.agent

Interface ExecutionCommand.KeyNames

  • Enclosing class:
    ExecutionCommand

    public static interface ExecutionCommand.KeyNames
    Contains key name strings. These strings are used inside maps incapsulated inside command.

        @Deprecated
static final String REPO_VERSION_ID
        Deprecated. 
        When installing packages, optionally provide the row id the version is for in order to precisely match response data.

      • VERSION

        static final String VERSION
